en.自动续费服务声明内容:
Payment: automatic renewal products include monthly membership / quarterly membership / annual membership. After you confirm your purchase, the fee will be deducted from your Apple iTunes account;
Renew membership: the fee will be deducted every month according to the time you purchase. Apple will automatically deduct the fee from your iTunes account. After success, the validity period will be automatically extended by one cycle;
Cancel renewal: if you need to cancel renewal, please manually turn off the automatic renewal function in iTunes / Apple ID settings management 24 hours before the expiration of the current subscription cycle. If you cancel within 24 hours before the expiration, the subscription fee will be charged.

en.参与用户体验反馈服务协议:
      Welcome to join the User Feedback Project. In order to improve the user experience of the product, we need to collect some user data (including terminal attribute data and product use data), summarize and analyze these data, so as to continuously improve the operation experience and operation performance of the product and improve the functional design, Launch new functions and services that are helpful to users. Without your permission, the software will not disclose information or provide it to third parties; This agreement is an integral part of participating in the user experience feedback. Once you select [participating in user experience feedback] [options similar to the "agree" button] and carry out subsequent operations, you agree to abide by all the provisions of this agreement. If you have any questions, comments or suggestions, please contact us in any of the following ways:
1. Email:【 2146185892@qq.com 】；
2. Customer service hotline: [4006530189] (service time: 9:00-24:00).
Please read the specific contents of the user feedback project carefully
1. Scope of application
1) Equipment attributes, such as operating system, hardware version, equipment setting, equipment carrier, equipment installation application, equipment advertisement identifier, etc;
2) In addition to terminal information, we also need to collect some specific data related to operation behavior, such as specific applicable behavior in your interaction with the product, current function name, etc;
3) we promise that no personal identity or privacy data will be involved in this plan, including name, address, e-mail, financial information, payment information, ID number, non-public telephone directory or contacts.
2. Use of information
After we have collected your relevant information, we may conduct statistical analysis on the relevant information and use the summary analysis results in one or more of the following forms:
1) Improve the functional experience of the product by analyzing the results;
2) Other application behaviors based on statistical results.
3. Storage of information
The information and materials about you collected by the software will be stored on the servers of the software and / or its affiliates. These information and materials may be transmitted to your country, region or overseas where the information and materials collected by the software are located, and accessed, stored and displayed overseas.
4. Information security
1) The software will not disclose your information to untrusted third parties.
2) Disclose to a third party or an administrative or judicial organ in accordance with the relevant provisions of the law or the requirements of the administrative or judicial organ;
3) If you violate relevant Chinese laws, regulations or relevant rules, you need to disclose it to a third party.
5. You shall not use the user feedback service in any way or for any purpose that will violate national and local laws and regulations, industry practices and social public ethics, and affect, damage or may affect or damage the interests of the software;
6. You understand and acknowledge that we reserve the right to modify, cancel or enhance one or more functions or all services of the user feedback service at any time. If the functions are modified or enhanced, we have the right to require you to use the latest updated version; At that time, we will notify you in advance by publishing announcements on the appropriate page in the software or sending notices on the website;
7. If any provision of this agreement is invalid or unenforceable in whole or in part for any reason, or violates any applicable law, such provision shall be deemed to be deleted, but the remaining provisions of this Agreement shall remain valid and binding;
8. The terms of this Agreement shall be governed by the laws of the people's Republic of China. In case of any dispute during the implementation of the terms of this agreement, both parties shall negotiate and solve it in time. If the negotiation fails, either party may directly bring a lawsuit to the people's Court of Yuelu District, Changsha.
